  "texts": [
    "To mitigate this, we tailor prompts for each type of relation to enhance the model's comprehension.",
    "Specifically, we leverage GPT-4 (OpenAI, 2023) with Web UI to craft prompts based on a simple slot-filling template designed for GPT-3.5, enabling it to recognize specific relations from the textual context.",
